		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The cool thing about math is just that you are thinking about things in a very logical way and because of this is applies to almost everything. When you code things it important to think in very precise ways... math helps with this. If you are doing something very specific then you might need math. <br /><br />In the original Doom for PC and Wolfenstein they used special techniques to give the illusion of 3D. These are areas which you would benefit from having a good math background. <br /><br />If you want to get good at math just find some free tutoring online community and volunteer. Teaching others is one of the fastest ways of learning new things. <br /><br />Oh by the way.... math major here. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

